"{\"uid\": \"billboard.com-pro-phoenix-olympics-closing-ceremony-performance-how\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"\\\"The performance has opened a lot of doors already and we are still seeing the impact in real time,\\\" says one of the band's managers, Matt Sadie.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 145, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The performance\", \"from\": 1, \"to\": 16}, {\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 28, \"to\": 33}, {\"ngram\": \"doors\", \"from\": 37, \"to\": 42}, {\"ngram\": \"the impact\", \"from\": 75, \"to\": 85}, {\"ngram\": \"real time\", \"from\": 89, \"to\": 98}, {\"ngram\": \"the band's managers\", \"from\": 113, \"to\": 132}, {\"ngram\": \"Matt Sadie\", \"from\": 134, \"to\": 144}]}, {\"sentence\": \"ByDan Rys This summer, nothing has been bigger than the Paris Olympics.\", \"from\": 147, \"to\": 219, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"ByDan Rys\", \"from\": 147, \"to\": 156}, {\"ngram\": \"nothing\", \"from\": 170, \"to\": 177}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris Olympics\", \"from\": 199, \"to\": 217}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The global games - held across 17 days from late July through last Sunday's Closing Ceremony - set all kinds of records.\", \"from\": 220, \"to\": 340, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The global games\", \"from\": 220, \"to\": 236}, {\"ngram\": \"17 days\", \"from\": 251, \"to\": 258}, {\"ngram\": \"late July\", \"from\": 264, \"to\": 273}, {\"ngram\": \"last Sunday's Closing Ceremony\", \"from\": 282, \"to\": 312}, {\"ngram\": \"all kinds\", \"from\": 319, \"to\": 328}, {\"ngram\": \"records\", \"from\": 332, \"to\": 339}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They drew an average U.S.daily viewershipof 30.6 million, an 82% jump from the 2021 Tokyo Games, and created worldwide stars out of some of the top athletes on the planet.\", \"from\": 341, \"to\": 512, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an 82% jump\", \"from\": 399, \"to\": 410}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2021 Tokyo Games\", \"from\": 416, \"to\": 436}, {\"ngram\": \"stars\", \"from\": 460, \"to\": 465}, {\"ngram\": \"the top athletes\", \"from\": 481, \"to\": 497}, {\"ngram\": \"the planet\", \"from\": 501, \"to\": 511}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Paris Games culminated in that star-studded Closing Ceremony, which featured a huge performance headlined by French band Phoenix in the iconic Stade de France, with onstage assists fromAir,Vampire Weekend'sEzra Koenigand French producerKavinsky, among others.\", \"from\": 514, \"to\": 777, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 627, \"end\": 633, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.5426881442445947, \"rank\": 0.8344453102595133, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}, {\"begin\": 639, \"end\": 646, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phoenix_Raceway\", \"score\": 0.9982038399311209, \"rank\": 0.0017986203862640916, \"text\": \"Phoenix\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phoenix_Raceway\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phoenix_Raceway\"}, {\"begin\": 661, \"end\": 676, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Stade de France\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\"}, {\"begin\": 707, \"end\": 722, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vampire_Weekend\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.023295909958802e-51, \"text\": \"Vampire Weekend\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q215380\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vampire_Weekend\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vampire_Weekend\"}, {\"begin\": 739, \"end\": 745, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.5426881442445947, \"rank\": 0.8344453102595133, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The Paris Games\", \"from\": 514, \"to\": 529}, {\"ngram\": \"that star-studded Closing Ceremony\", \"from\": 544, \"to\": 578}, {\"ngram\": \"a huge performance\", \"from\": 595, \"to\": 613}, {\"ngram\": \"onstage\", \"from\": 683, \"to\": 690}, {\"ngram\": \"others\", \"from\": 770, \"to\": 776}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Closing Ceremony drew more than 20 million viewers in the U.S. alone, while its effect led to a giant surge in streams and sales for Phoenix and Kavinsky in particular: Streams for Phoenix'scatalog jumped 86%over the prior week following the performance, while Kavinsky's \\\"Nightcall\\\" broke the record for most Shazams in a single day and saw itsstreams grow 74%.\", \"from\": 778, \"to\": 1144, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 915, \"end\": 922, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phoenix_Raceway\", \"score\": 0.9982038399311209, \"rank\": 0.0017986203862640916, \"text\": \"Phoenix\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phoenix_Raceway\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phoenix_Raceway\"}, {\"begin\": 963, \"end\": 970, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phoenix_Raceway\", \"score\": 0.9982038399311209, \"rank\": 0.0017986203862640916, \"text\": \"Phoenix\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phoenix_Raceway\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phoenix_Raceway\"}, {\"begin\": 1043, \"end\": 1051, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kavinsky\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Kavinsky\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kavinsky\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kavinsky\"}, {\"begin\": 1092, \"end\": 1099, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shazam_(application)\", \"score\": 0.996933274287284, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Shazams\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wi