: 1218}, {\"ngram\": \"the past few decades\", \"from\": 1222, \"to\": 1242}, {\"ngram\": \"all time\", \"from\": 1279, \"to\": 1287}, {\"ngram\": \"their manager\", \"from\": 1303, \"to\": 1316}, {\"ngram\": \"the title ofBillboard's Executive\", \"from\": 1339, \"to\": 1372}, {\"ngram\": \"the Week\", \"from\": 1376, \"to\": 1384}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Here, Sadie talks about all the work that went into the performance behind the scenes, the platform of performing in front of an estimated 800 million people worldwide and what this means for the band.\", \"from\": 1386, \"to\": 1587, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Sadie\", \"from\": 1392, \"to\": 1397}, {\"ngram\": \"all the work\", \"from\": 1410, \"to\": 1422}, {\"ngram\": \"the performance\", \"from\": 1438, \"to\": 1453}, {\"ngram\": \"the scenes\", \"from\": 1461, \"to\": 1471}, {\"ngram\": \"the platform\", \"from\": 1473, \"to\": 1485}, {\"ngram\": \"front\", \"from\": 1503, \"to\": 1508}, {\"ngram\": \"an estimated 800 million people\", \"from\": 1512, \"to\": 1543}, {\"ngram\": \"the band\", \"from\": 1578, \"to\": 1586}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There have been so many times over the years when we - the management team and Branco, Christian, Thomas and Deck in the band - have all worked very, very closely to bring their special vision to fruition,\\\" Sadie says.\", \"from\": 1588, \"to\": 1807, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1676, \"end\": 1685, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christian_music\", \"score\": 0.745961535093666, \"rank\": 0.3351411749999971, \"text\": \"Christian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christian_music\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christian_music\"}, {\"begin\": 1687, \"end\": 1693, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_the_Tank_Engine\", \"score\": 0.7722460256442151, \"rank\": 0.29023895111719766, \"text\": \"Thomas\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_the_Tank_Engine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_the_Tank_Engine\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the years\", \"from\": 1624, \"to\": 1633}, {\"ngram\": \"the management team\", \"from\": 1644, \"to\": 1663}, {\"ngram\": \"Branco\", \"from\": 1668, \"to\": 1674}, {\"ngram\": \"Deck\", \"from\": 1698, \"to\": 1702}, {\"ngram\": \"the band\", \"from\": 1706, \"to\": 1714}, {\"ngram\": \"their special vision\", \"from\": 1761, \"to\": 1781}, {\"ngram\": \"fruition\", \"from\": 1785, \"to\": 1793}, {\"ngram\": \"Sadie\", \"from\": 1796, \"to\": 1801}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The Olympics performance felt like a real crowning moment in Phoenix's career, and I am thrilled to have been a part of it.\\\"\", \"from\": 1808, \"to\": 1933, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1870, \"end\": 1877, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phoenix_Raceway\", \"score\": 0.9982038399311209, \"rank\": 0.0017986203862640916, \"text\": \"Phoenix\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phoenix_Raceway\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phoenix_Raceway\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The Olympics performance\", \"from\": 1809, \"to\": 1833}, {\"ngram\": \"a real crowning moment\", \"from\": 1844, \"to\": 1866}, {\"ngram\": \"a part\", \"from\": 1919, \"to\": 1925}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This week, Phoenix performed in Paris for the Olympics Closing Ceremony, a huge event for the band and the country.\", \"from\": 1935, \"to\": 2050, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1946, \"end\": 1953, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phoenix_Raceway\", \"score\": 0.9982038399311209, \"rank\": 0.0017986203862640916, \"text\": \"Phoenix\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phoenix_Raceway\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phoenix_Raceway\"}, {\"begin\": 1967, \"end\": 1972, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0693233627115248e-13, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympics Closing Ceremony\", \"from\": 1977, \"to\": 2006}, {\"ngram\": \"a huge event\", \"from\": 2008, \"to\": 2020}, {\"ngram\": \"the band\", \"from\": 2025, \"to\": 2033}, {\"ngram\": \"the country\", \"from\": 2038, \"to\": 2049}]}, {\"sentence\": \"How did that come together, and what key decisions did you make to help make that happen?\", \"from\": 2051, \"to\": 2140, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"what key decisions\", \"from\": 2083, \"to\": 2101}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As soon as Paris was given the Olympics for 2024 back in 2017, we immediately identified the opportunity internally.\", \"from\": 2142, \"to\": 2258, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2153, \"end\": 2158, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0693233627115248e-13, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 2169, \"to\": 2181}, {\"ngram\": \"the opportunity\", \"from\": 2231, \"to\": 2246}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It felt very logical that a band of their international stature, from near Paris and largely based there, should have a place in the Olympics.\", \"from\": 2259, \"to\": 2401, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2334, \"end\": 2339, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0693233627115248e-13, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a band\", \"from\": 2285, \"to\": 2291}, {\"ngram\": \"their international stature\", \"from\": 2295, \"to\": 2322}, {\"ngram\": \"a place\", \"from\": 2377, \"to\": 2384}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 2388, \"to\": 2400}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Opening and Closing Ceremonies were definitely top of the list.\", \"from\": 2402, \"to\": 2469, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The Opening and Closing Ceremonies\", \"from\": 2402, \"to\": 2436}, {\"ngram\": \"the list\", \"from\": 2460, \"to\": 2468}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Clearly, the Olympics team were not at the stage of picking acts for the ceremonies in 2017, but around two years ago, alongside my counterpart in France,Laurence Muller, and the band's agent in France,Sofiene Bijaouifrom Corida, we identified who the powers that be were and began conversations.\", \"from\": 2471, \"to\": 2767, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2618, \"end\": 2624, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9999330219392032, \"rank\": 6.355098508766304e-05, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}, {\"begin\": 2666, \"end\": 2672, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9999330219392032, \"rank\": 6.355098508766304e-05, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympics team\", \"from\": 2480, \"to\": 2497}, {\"ngram\": \"the stage\", \"from\": 2510, \"to\": 2519}, {\"ngram\": \"acts\", \"from\": 2531, \"to\": 2535}, {\"ngram\": \"the ceremonies\", \"from\": 2540, \"to\": 2554}, {\"ngram\": \"my counterpart\", \"from\": 2600, \"to\": 2614}, {\"ngram\": \"Laurence Muller\", \"from\": 2625, \"to\": 2640}, {\"ngram\": \"the band's agent\", \"from\": 2646, \"to\": 2662}, {\"ngram\": \"Sofiene Bijaouifrom Corida\", \"from\": 2673, \"to\": 2699}, {\"ngram\": \"the powers\", \"from\": 2719, \"to\": 2729}, {\"ngram\": \"conversations\", \"from\": 2753, \"to\": 2766}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There was a lot of perseverance from everyone on the team.\", \"from\": 2768, \"to\": 2826, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 2778, \"to\": 2783}, {\"ngram\": \"perseverance\", \"from\": 2787, \"to\": 2799}, {\"ngram\": \"everyone\", \"from\": 2805, \"to\": 2813}, {\"ngram\": \"the team\", \"from\": 2817, \"to\": 2825}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In the meantime, last year we planned the band's touring to keep them in Europe over this summer, leaving gaps in the schedule where the Opening and Closing Ceremonies were.\", \"from\": 2827, \"to\": 3000, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the meantime\", \"from\": 2830, \"to\": 2842}, {\"ngram\": \"the band's touring\", \"from\": 2865, \"to\": 2883}, {\"ngram\": \"Europe\", \"from\": 2900, \"to\": 2906}, {\"ngram\": \"this summer\", \"from\": 2912, \"to\": 2923}, {\"ngram\": \"gaps\", \"from\": 2933, \"to\": 2937}, {\"ngram\": \"the schedule\", \"from\": 2941, \"to\": 2953}, {\"ngram\": \"the Opening and Closing Ceremonies\", \"from\": 2960, \"to\": 2994}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This allowed the flexibility needed in case the call came, which it eventually did.\", \"from\": 3001, \"to\": 3084, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the flexibility\", \"from\": 3014, \"to\": 3029}, {\"ngram\": \"case\", \"from\": 3040, \"to\": 3044}, {\"ngram\": \"the call\", \"from\": 3045, \"to\": 3053}]}, {\"sentence\": \"What are the considerations when putting an act onto an event as prestigious as the Closing Ceremony?\", \"from\": 3086, \"to\": 3187, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the considerations\", \"from\": 3095, \"to\": 3113}, {\"ngram\": \"an act\", \"from\": 3127, \"to\": 3133}, {\"ngram\": \"an event\", \"from\": 3139, \"to\": 3147}, {\"ngram\": \"the Closing Ceremony\", \"from\": 3166, \"to\": 3186}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Was there any hesitation or was it an automatic yes?\", \"from\": 3188, \"to\": 3240, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"any hesitation\", \"from\": 3198, \"to\": 3212}]}, {\"sentence\": \"How do you say no?\", \"from\": 3242, \"to\": 3260, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Given the scale of the opportunity and the very natural connection in being a French band from the area, it was as close to an automatic yes as one can get.\", \"from\": 3261, \"to\": 3417, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3339, \"end\": 3345, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.5426881442445947, \"rank\": 0.8344453102595133, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the scale\", \"from\": 3267, \"to\": 3276}, {\"ngram\": \"the opportunity\", \"from\": 3280, \"to\": 3295}, {\"ngram\": \"the very natural connection\", \"from\": 3300, \"to\": 3327}, {\"ngram\": \"the area\", \"from\": 3356, \"to\": 3364}, {\"ngram\": \"one\", \"from\": 3405, \"to\": 3408}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In our conversations with the Olympics team, we were immediately given a lot of independence in putting their set together - there was simply the remit that the performance had to feel like a party for the athletes and that we had 15-17 minutes to play with.\", \"from\": 3418, \"to\": 3676, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"our conversations\", \"from\": 3421, \"to\": 3438}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics team\", \"from\": 3444, \"to\": 3461}, {\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 3489, \"to\": 3494}, {\"ngram\": \"independence\", \"from\": 3498, \"to\": 3510}, {\"ngram\": \"their set\", \"from\": 3522, \"to\": 3531}, {\"ngram\": \"the remit\", \"from\": 3560, \"to\": 3569}, {\"ngram\": \"the performance\", \"from\": 3575, \"to\": 3590}, {\"ngram\": \"a party\", \"from\": 3608, \"to\": 3615}, {\"ngram\": \"the athletes\", \"from\": 3620, \"to\": 3632}, {\"ngram\": \"15-17 minutes\", \"from\": 3649, \"to\": 3662}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Knowing that the band would be playing to a global audience of around 800 million, the priority for us was to put a show together which would have the potential to appeal to people who'd never heard of Phoenix before and would remind those who had why they have continued to be one of the most beloved artists of the last 20 years.\", \"from\": 3677, \"to\": 4008, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3879, \"end\": 3886, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phoenix_Raceway\", \"score\": 0.9982038399311209, \"rank\": 0.0017986203862640916, \"text\": \"Phoenix\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phoenix_Raceway\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phoenix_Raceway\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the band\", \"from\": 3690, \"to\": 3698}, {\"ngram\": \"a global audience\", \"from\": 3719, \"to\": 3736}, {\"ngram\": \"the priority\", \"from\": 3760, \"to\": 3772}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 3777, \"to\": 3779}, {\"ngram\": \"a show\", \"from\": 3791, \"to\": 3797}, {\"ngram\": \"the potential\", \"from\": 3824, \"to\": 3837}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 3851, \"to\": 3857}, {\"ngram\": \"the most beloved artists\", \"from\": 3962, \"to\": 3986}, {\"ngram\": \"the last 20 years\", \"from\": 3990, \"to\": 4007}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We immediately felt the pre-conditions of the set given to us by the Olympics meant that this was a no-brainer.\", \"from\": 4009, \"to\": 4120, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the pre\", \"from\": 4029, \"to\": 4036}, {\"ngram\": \"conditions\", \"from\": 4037, \"to\": 4047}, {\"ngram\": \"the set\", \"from\": 4051, \"to\": 4058}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 4068, \"to\": 4070}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 4074, \"to\": 4086}, {\"ngram\": \"a no-brainer\", \"from\": 4107, \"to\": 4119}]}, {\"sentence\": \"How did you prepare for this differently than any other gig?\", \"from\": 4122, \"to\": 4182, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"any other gig\", \"from\": 4168, \"to\": 4181}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Pretty much every aspect of this show required preparations that were different to a normal show for the band.\", \"from\": 4184, \"to\": 4294, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"every aspect\", \"from\": 4196, \"to\": 4208}, {\"ngram\": \"this show\", \"from\": 4212, \"to\": 4221}, {\"ngram\": \"preparations\", \"from\": 4231, \"to\": 4243}, {\"ngram\": \"a normal show\", \"from\": 4267, \"to\": 4280}, {\"ngram\": \"the band\", \"from\": 4285, \"to\": 4293}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was very much non-stop from myself, Laurence and the rest of the team from the moment we got the green light.\", \"from\": 4295, \"to\": 4407, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the team\", \"from\": 4359, \"to\": 4367}, {\"ngram\": \"the moment\", \"from\": 4373, \"to\": 4383}, {\"ngram\": \"the green light\", \"from\": 4391, \"to\": 4406}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The band have not played a medley set of this kind before, so that was a challenge in itself.\", \"from\": 4409, \"to\": 4502, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The band\", \"from\": 4409, \"to\": 4417}, {\"ngram\": \"a medley set\", \"from\": 4434, \"to\": 4446}, {\"ngram\": \"this kind\", \"from\": 4450, \"to\": 4459}, {\"ngram\": \"a challenge\", \"from\": 4480, \"to\": 4491}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They knew they wanted to have some guests, so identifying them, getting them on board, and working through logistical gymnastics was pretty consuming for all.\", \"from\": 4503, \"to\": 4661, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"some guests\", \"from\": 4533, \"to\": 4544}, {\"ngram\": \"board\", \"from\": 4583, \"to\": 4588}, {\"ngram\": \"logistical gymnastics\", \"from\": 4610, \"to\": 4631}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For the band, having the acts they wanted to join them in Air, Kavinsky, Angele, Ezra Koenig of Vampire Weekend and VannDa, was a very different approach to a normal show but one they relished.\", \"from\": 4662, \"to\": 4855, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4743, \"end\": 4747, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ezra_Pound\", \"score\": 0.9999998941111754, \"rank\": 1.0587811405310884e-07, \"text\": \"Ezra\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ezra_Pound\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ezra_Pound\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the band\", \"from\": 4666, \"to\": 4674}, {\"ngram\": \"the acts\", \"from\": 4683, \"to\": 4691}, {\"ngram\": \"Air\", \"from\": 4720, \"to\": 4723}, {\"ngram\": \"Kavinsky\", \"from\": 4725, \"to\": 4733}, {\"ngram\": \"Angele\", \"from\": 4735, \"to\": 4741}, {\"ngram\": \"Vampire\", \"from\": 4758, \"to\": 4765}, {\"ngram\": \"a very different approach\", \"from\": 4790, \"to\": 4815}, {\"ngram\": \"a normal show\", \"from\": 4819, \"to\": 4832}, {\"ngram\": \"one\", \"from\": 4837, \"to\": 4840}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If you have seen them play before, you will know that the band have always put a lot of focus into the production at their live shows.\", \"from\": 4857, \"to\": 4991, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the band\", \"from\": 4911, \"to\": 4919}, {\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 4936, \"to\": 4941}, {\"ngram\": \"focus\", \"from\": 4945, \"to\": 4950}, {\"ngram\": \"the production\", \"from\": 4956, \"to\": 4970}, {\"ngram\": \"their live shows\", \"from\": 4974, \"to\": 4990}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They'd usually have the control and time to finesse it into something very special.\", \"from\": 4992, \"to\": 5075, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the control\", \"from\": 5012, \"to\": 5023}, {\"ngram\": \"time\", \"from\": 5028, \"to\": 5032}, {\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 5052, \"to\": 5061}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We had neither of those luxuries here; we were simply told, \\\"You will be playing on a stage in the middle of the stadium which is shaped like the world map - you will be playing in Africa.\\\"\", \"from\": 5076, \"to\": 5265, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"neither\", \"from\": 5083, \"to\": 5090}, {\"ngram\": \"those luxuries\", \"from\": 5094, \"to\": 5108}, {\"ngram\": \"a stage\", \"from\": 5160, \"to\": 5167}, {\"ngram\": \"the middle\", \"from\": 5171, \"to\": 5181}, {\"ngram\": \"the stadium\", \"from\": 5185, \"to\": 5196}, {\"ngram\": \"the world map\", \"from\": 5218, \"to\": 5231}, {\"ngram\": \"Africa\", \"from\": 5257, \"to\": 5263}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We worked closely with the team to create a scenario which would work for the band and their guest performers.\", \"from\": 5266, \"to\": 5376, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the team\", \"from\": 5289, \"to\": 5297}, {\"ngram\": \"a scenario\", \"from\": 5308, \"to\": 5318}, {\"ngram\": \"the band\", \"from\": 5340, \"to\": 5348}, {\"ngram\": \"their guest performers\", \"from\": 5353, \"to\": 5375}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Playing in a stadium is very different to a festival show or the sheds the band played at during their recent U.S. co-headline run withBeck, but it gave our brilliant lighting designerPierre Claudea huge scale of production elements to work with.\", \"from\": 5377, \"to\": 5623, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a stadium\", \"from\": 5388, \"to\": 5397}, {\"ngram\": \"a festival show\", \"from\": 5419, \"to\": 5434}, {\"ngram\": \"the sheds\", \"from\": 5438, \"to\": 5447}, {\"ngram\": \"the band\", \"from\": 5448, \"to\": 5456}, {\"ngram\": \"their recent U.S. co-headline run\", \"from\": 5474, \"to\": 5507}, {\"ngram\": \"our brilliant lighting designerPierre Claudea huge scale\", \"from\": 5530, \"to\": 5586}, {\"ngram\": \"production elements\", \"from\": 5590, \"to\": 5609}]}, {\"sentence\": \"His efforts to pull things together were truly herculean.\", \"from\": 5624, \"to\": 5681, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"His efforts\", \"from\": 5624, \"to\": 5635}, {\"ngram\": \"things\", \"from\": 5644, \"to\": 5650}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We have done plenty of live streams - from festivals and most recently with Air from the roof of the Charles De Gaulle Airport in Paris, but this was on a whole different scale, with over 80 cameras in the stadium capturing the show.\", \"from\": 5683, \"to\": 5916, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5784, \"end\": 5809, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charles_de_Gaulle_Airport\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Charles De Gaulle Airport\", \"types\": [\"Q1248784\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charles_de_Gaulle_Airport\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charles_de_Gaulle_Airport\"}, {\"begin\": 5813, \"end\": 5818, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0693233627115248e-13, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"plenty\", \"from\": 5696, \"to\": 5702}, {\"ngram\": \"live streams\", \"from\": 5706, \"to\": 5718}, {\"ngram\": \"festivals\", \"from\": 5726, \"to\": 5735}, {\"ngram\": \"Air\", \"from\": 5759, \"to\": 5762}, {\"ngram\": \"the roof\", \"from\": 5768, \"to\": 5776}, {\"ngram\": \"a whole different scale\", \"from\": 5836, \"to\": 5859}, {\"ngram\": \"over 80 cameras\", \"from\": 5866, \"to\": 5881}, {\"ngram\": \"the stadium\", \"from\": 5885, \"to\": 5896}, {\"ngram\": \"the show\", \"from\": 5907, \"to\": 5915}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We also were not in control of the direction during the livestream.\", \"from\": 5917, \"to\": 5984, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"control\", \"from\": 5937, \"to\": 5944}, {\"ngram\": \"the direction\", \"from\": 5948, \"to\": 5961}, {\"ngram\": \"the livestream\", \"from\": 5969, \"to\": 5983}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As a solution, Laurence brought inDavid Ctiborskyfrom Blogotheque, who'd worked closely with the band on various livestreams, to ensure that the various \\\"moments\\\" were filmed effectively, advising the team from the Olympics capturing it.\", \"from\": 5985, \"to\": 6222, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a solution\", \"from\": 5988, \"to\": 5998}, {\"ngram\": \"Laurence\", \"from\": 6000, \"to\": 6008}, {\"ngram\": \"inDavid Ctiborskyfrom Blogotheque\", \"from\": 6017, \"to\": 6050}, {\"ngram\": \"the band\", \"from\": 6078, \"to\": 6086}, {\"ngram\": \"various livestreams\", \"from\": 6090, \"to\": 6109}, {\"ngram\": \"the various \\\"moments\", \"from\": 6126, \"to\": 6146}, {\"ngram\": \"the team\", \"from\": 6182, \"to\": 6190}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 6196, \"to\": 6208}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We also were conscious that this was being broadcast around the world via local broadcasters, so talking points on each of the songs and artists involved was critical promotionally.\", \"from\": 6223, \"to\": 6404, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 6283, \"to\": 6292}, {\"ngram\": \"local broadcasters\", \"from\": 6297, \"to\": 6315}, {\"ngram\": \"talking points\", \"from\": 6320, \"to\": 6334}, {\"ngram\": \"the songs\", \"from\": 6346, \"to\": 6355}, {\"ngram\": \"artists\", \"from\": 6360, \"to\": 6367}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Outside of the show itself, promoting it was very different from any other show.\", \"from\": 6406, \"to\": 6486, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the show\", \"from\": 6417, \"to\": 6425}, {\"ngram\": \"any other show\", \"from\": 6471, \"to\": 6485}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Rather than the usual heavy promotion into a show, news of their performance was technically embargoed until the last minute, despite the odd leak here and there.\", \"from\": 6487, \"to\": 6649, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the usual heavy promotion\", \"from\": 6499, \"to\": 6524}, {\"ngram\": \"a show\", \"from\": 6530, \"to\": 6536}, {\"ngram\": \"news\", \"from\": 6538, \"to\": 6542}, {\"ngram\": \"their performance\", \"from\": 6546, \"to\": 6563}, {\"ngram\": \"the last minute\", \"from\": 6596, \"to\": 6611}, {\"ngram\": \"the odd leak\", \"from\": 6621, \"to\": 6633}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This meant that we had to be reactive with media after the fact, which we were ready to do via our PR -Jen Appelof The Oriel andNathalie Ridardof Ephelide - our digital marketing team, Dream Team, and the team at C3 Management.\", \"from\": 6650, \"to\": 6877, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6835, \"end\": 6845, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FC_Barcelona\", \"score\": 0.958246981941863, \"rank\": 0.037990572521805724, \"text\": \"Dream Team\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FC_Barcelona\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FC_Barcelona\"}, {\"begin\": 6863, \"end\": 6865, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/C3_carbon_fixation\", \"score\": 0.9999999952442522, \"rank\": 4.7420599672346005e-09, \"text\": \"C3\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/C3_carbon_fixation\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/C3_carbon_fixation\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"media\", \"from\": 6693, \"to\": 6698}, {\"ngram\": \"the fact\", \"from\": 6705, \"to\": 6713}, {\"ngram\": \"our PR\", \"from\": 6745, \"to\": 6751}, {\"ngram\": \"Appelof\", \"from\": 6757, \"to\": 6764}, {\"ngram\": \"our digital marketing team\", \"from\": 6807, \"to\": 6833}, {\"ngram\": \"the team\", \"from\": 6851, \"to\": 6859}]}, {\"sentence\": \"With the band appearing onstage with Kavinsky and Air, and the closing ceremony also featuring a medley ofJusticesongs, what does it all say about the importance of electronic music to French culture?\", \"from\": 6879, \"to\": 7079, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6916, \"end\": 6924, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kavinsky\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Kavinsky\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kavinsky\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kavinsky\"}, {\"begin\": 7064, \"end\": 7078, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Culture_of_France\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"French culture\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Culture_of_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Culture_of_France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the band\", \"from\": 6884, \"to\": 6892}, {\"ngram\": \"Air\", \"from\": 6929, \"to\": 6932}, {\"ngram\": \"the closing ceremony\", \"from\": 6938, \"to\": 6958}, {\"ngram\": \"a medley ofJusticesongs\", \"from\": 6974, \"to\": 6997}, {\"ngram\": \"the importance\", \"from\": 7026, \"to\": 7040}, {\"ngram\": \"electronic music\", \"from\": 7044, \"to\": 7060}]}, {\"sentence\": \"To their credit, in choosing artists from the \\\"French Touch\\\" movement, the creative team behind the Closing Ceremony identified something very special that France brought to the world.Daft Punk, Air, Phoenix, Justice and many more have had a huge, and sometimes unsung, impact on music globally, not just in the electronic space.\", \"from\": 7081, \"to\": 7410, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7128, \"end\": 7140, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_house\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.7218203599355826e-36, \"text\": \"French Touch\", \"types\": [\"Q188451\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_house\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_house\"}, {\"begin\": 7237, \"end\": 7243, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9999330219392032, \"rank\": 6.355098508766304e-05, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"their credit\", \"from\": 7084, \"to\": 7096}, {\"ngram\": \"artists\", \"from\": 7110, \"to\": 7117}, {\"ngram\": \"the creative team\", \"from\": 7152, \"to\": 7169}, {\"ngram\": \"the Closing Ceremony\", \"from\": 7177, \"to\": 7197}, {\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 7209, \"to\": 7218}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 7255, \"to\": 7264}, {\"ngram\": \"Daft Punk\", \"from\": 7265, \"to\": 7274}, {\"ngram\": \"a huge, and sometimes unsung, impact\", \"from\": 7321, \"to\": 7357}, {\"ngram\": \"music\", \"from\": 7361, \"to\": 7366}, {\"ngram\": \"the electronic space\", \"from\": 7389, \"to\": 7409}]}, {\"sentence\": \"To my mind, it's one of the country's greatest present-day cultural exports.\", \"from\": 7411, \"to\": 7487, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my mind\", \"from\": 7414, \"to\": 7421}, {\"ngram\": \"the country's greatest present-day cultural exports\", \"from\": 7435, \"to\": 7486}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Highlighting it in the ceremony really allowed them to celebrate something uniquely French but also globally relevant and ultimately timeless.\", \"from\": 7488, \"to\": 7630, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the ceremony\", \"from\": 7507, \"to\": 7519}, {\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 7553, \"to\": 7562}]}, {\"sentence\": \"What position does a performance like this put the band in, in terms of their next moves?\", \"from\": 7632, \"to\": 7721, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"What position\", \"from\": 7632, \"to\": 7645}, {\"ngram\": \"a performance\", \"from\": 7651, \"to\": 7664}, {\"ngram\": \"the band\", \"from\": 7679, \"to\": 7687}, {\"ngram\": \"terms\", \"from\": 7695, \"to\": 7700}, {\"ngram\": \"their next moves\", \"from\": 7704, \"to\": 7720}]}, {\"sentence\": \"How do they capitalize on the moment?\", \"from\": 7722, \"to\": 7759, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the moment\", \"from\": 7748, \"to\": 7758}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Clearly this has been a huge watershed moment for the band globally.\", \"from\": 7761, \"to\": 7829, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a huge watershed moment\", \"from\": 7783, \"to\": 7806}, {\"ngram\": \"the band\", \"from\": 7811, \"to\": 7819}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Every metric has shown that this week, notably seven of the top 11 songs on Shazam this week are from their set, including Kavinsky's \\\"Nightcall\\\" receiving the most Shazams of any song in a day ever.\", \"from\": 7830, \"to\": 8029, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7906, \"end\": 7912, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Characters_of_the_DC_Extended_Universe\", \"score\": 0.9999991609714807, \"rank\": 8.390292025535228e-07, \"text\": \"Shazam\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Characters_of_the_DC_Extended_Universe\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Characters_of_the_DC_Extended_Universe\"}, {\"begin\": 7953, \"end\": 7961, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kavinsky\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Kavinsky\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kavinsky\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kavinsky\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Every metric\", \"from\": 7830, \"to\": 7842}, {\"ngram\": \"the top 11 songs\", \"from\": 7886, \"to\": 7902}, {\"ngram\": \"their set\", \"from\": 7932, \"to\": 7941}, {\"ngram\": \"the most Shazams\", \"from\": 7986, \"to\": 8002}, {\"ngram\": \"any song\", \"from\": 8006, \"to\": 8014}, {\"ngram\": \"a day\", \"from\": 8018, \"to\": 8023}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We have seen serious growth on socials and streaming numbers, alongside a vast amount of media coverage.\", \"from\": 8030, \"to\": 8134, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"serious growth\", \"from\": 8043, \"to\": 8057}, {\"ngram\": \"socials\", \"from\": 8061, \"to\": 8068}, {\"ngram\": \"streaming numbers\", \"from\": 8073, \"to\": 8090}, {\"ngram\": \"a vast amount\", \"from\": 8102, \"to\": 8115}, {\"ngram\": \"media coverage\", \"from\": 8119, \"to\": 8133}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There is no doubt that a huge number of people have discovered the band, and I am sure many others have enjoyed being reminded of some of their favorite songs from the last couple decades.\", \"from